abstract: YONKERS, Sept. 7--The Hilltop Trot, the fifth of eight 1966 harness races offering minimum gross purses of $100,000 at Yonkers Raceway, is set for tomorrow night. And even though eight standardbreds will go postward in this 1 -mile test for 4-year-olds, the betting on the event will be restricted to win only.
